        "id": 1806960
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-12-04T23:30:06Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "There\u0027s no straightforward way to add interdependent options with argparse afaict.\n\nI did make this friendlier though by printing the help message followed by the specific error. No stacktrace because of SystemExit - which is what parse_args raises afaict. PTAL.",
      "parentUuid": "0db74270_a396a27c",
      "revId": "5fa2bad2ce87ef0b880edf07e04c34fbcb7f26c4",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889"
    },
    {
